    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Garten of Banban, now in VR!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience Garten of Banban for the first time in Virtual Reality in this brand new story! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel full world immersion as you interact with the environments and characters as you attempt to escape from the kindergarten.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/226449c7e7b10f54ba6e02b650e11a80.poster.avif?t=1741869197\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/226449c7e7b10f54ba6e02b650e11a80.webm?t=1741869197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/226449c7e7b10f54ba6e02b650e11a80.mp4?t=1741869197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Brand New Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garten of Banban: Distorting Clay is not a VR remake of the original series. Rather, it's its own special story that takes place inside of Banban's Kindergarten.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/6c1becb36ca7c9e2944216a6ad5414c2.poster.avif?t=1741869197\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/6c1becb36ca7c9e2944216a6ad5414c2.webm?t=1741869197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/6c1becb36ca7c9e2944216a6ad5414c2.mp4?t=1741869197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique mechanics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garten of Banban VR: Distorting Clay features the shapeshifting mechanic, allowing you to shift into familiar monsters that contain their own unique gameplay abilities and exclusive mechanics! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/fc08cf71049230d96e38bf30dbdea350.poster.avif?t=1741869197\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/fc08cf71049230d96e38bf30dbdea350.webm?t=1741869197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200520/extras/fc08cf71049230d96e38bf30dbdea350.mp4?t=1741869197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
